.TH DEBCONF-TRANSLATION-MANAGER 1 "March 2026" "0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
debconf-translation-manager \- manage translations of Debian debconf templates
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B debconf-translation-manager
[\fI\-\-no\-gui\fR] [\fI\-\-json\fR] [\fI\-q\fR] [\fI\-\-version\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B debconf-translation-manager
is a GTK4/libadwaita application for managing translations of Debian
debconf templates. It provides a template browser, PO editor with
side-by-side view, BTS bug filing workflow, DDTSS integration,
review board with l10n.debian.org data, and translation statistics.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-no\-gui
Run in CLI mode without the graphical interface. Print translation
statistics and exit.
.TP
.B \-\-json
Output statistics in JSON format (implies \-\-no\-gui).
.TP
.B \-q, \-\-quiet
Quiet mode, minimal output (implies \-\-no\-gui).
.TP
.B \-\-version
Show version number and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/debconf\-translation\-manager/settings.json
User preferences (translator name, email, language, SMTP settings).
.TP
.I ~/.config/debconf\-translation\-manager/submission_log.json
Log of previously submitted bug reports.
.SH AUTHOR
Daniel Nylander <daniel@danielnylander.se>
.SH SEE ALSO
